&lt;li&gt;Secure in-kind support such as GPU compute, cloud credits, data infrastructure, and engineering collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships with companies across the AI, cloud, developer tooling, and research infrastructure ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with internal technical teams to understand infrastructure needs and translate them into partnership opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure compliance with emerging AI and data regulations globally.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Structure win-win collaborations that provide value to partners while accelerating FirstPrinciples’ research and development projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
